---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us" description="Learn more about Entryway Essentials and our mission.">
  <section class="py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-medium font-display text-base-900 leading-tight">About Us</h1>
      <div class="prose prose-base md:prose-lg prose-base-600 mt-12">
        <p>Welcome to <strong>Entryway Essentials</strong>, your number one source for all things related to home entryway design and organization. We're dedicated to providing you the very best of tips, inspiration, and product reviews, with an emphasis on functionality, aesthetics, and minimalist design.</p>
        
        <p>Founded in 2024, Entryway Essentials has come a long way from its beginnings. When we first started out, our passion for creating welcoming and organized spaces drove us to start our own blog so that Entryway Essentials can offer you the best advice for your home.</p>

        <p>We hope you enjoy our articles as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        
        <p>Sincerely,</p>
        <p>The Entryway Essentials Team</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
